<h4 id="archive-files">Archive files</h4>

<p>Last semester, you created a Semester 1 folder. It has all of your work in it. You should offload that onto a USB key for safe keeping. Itâ€™s even a good idea to put it on two USB keys. Keep each at a different place, so you donâ€™t lose them.</p>

<h4 id="update-all-your-adobe-apps">Update all your Adobe Apps.</h4>

<p>Go to the Creative Cloud icon in your menu bar. Make sure to run any updates that are there.</p>

<h4 id="mouse--adaptor">Mouse &amp; Adaptor</h4>

<p>Bring a mouse to every class. Itâ€™s not efficient to work on your trackpad. Just keep the mouse in your bag. Optionally, you could <a href="https://www.apple.com/ca/shop/product/MMEL2AM/A/thunderbolt-3-usb-c-to-thunderbolt-2-adapter" title="Thunderbolt 3 USB-C to Thunderbolt 2 adaptor" target="_blank">purchase this adaptor</a> to connect to displays. Bring a pair of earphones/headphones to listen to tutorials.</p>
